    "We employ temporal convolutional network (TCN), an effective deep learning model, combined with interval estimation algorithms to generate a reliable forecasting framework (containing point forecasts and interval forecasts).",
    "Third, this is the first study to construct a trading strategy based on interval constraints.",
    "Interval restrictions are added to the general point forecast-based trading strategy to avoid irrational investments in high volatility periods or to generate huge returns.",
